---
import T from '../T.astro';
---

          <!-- ============ MASJID FLOW ============ -->
          <div class="qa-screen" data-screen="masjid-start">
            <span class="qa-badge">Masjid</span>
            <h3 class="qa-question">
              <span data-lang-text="en">Can I enter the Masjid during haiz?</span>
              <span data-lang-text="ru">Haiz mein Masjid mein ja sakti hoon?</span>
              <span data-lang-text="ur">حیض میں مسجد میں جا سکتی ہوں؟</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="qa-answer">
              <div class="qa-answer-icon warning">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M12 7v6M12 16v1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="qa-answer-title">
                <span data-lang-text="en">Entering Masjid is HARAM</span>
                <span data-lang-text="ru">Masjid Mein Jaana HARAM Hai</span>
                <span data-lang-text="ur">مسجد میں جانا HARAM ہے</span>
              </h3>
              <p class="qa-answer-text">
                <span data-lang-text="en">It is haram for a woman in haiz to enter the Masjid. This includes sitting, staying, or performing i'tikaaf.</span>
                <span data-lang-text="ru">Haiz wali aurat ka Masjid mein jaana haram hai. Is mein baithna, rehna, ya i'tikaaf karna sab shamil hai.</span>
                <span data-lang-text="ur">حیض والی عورت کا مسجد میں جانا حرام ہے۔ اس میں بیٹھنا، رہنا، یا اعتکاف کرنا سب شامل ہے۔</span>
              </p>
              <div class="qa-ruling">
                <span class="qa-ruling-label"><T en="Exception" ru="Exception" ur="Exception" /></span>
                <p>
                  <span data-lang-text="en">If the Masjid is the only path and there's no alternative, you may pass through quickly without sitting.</span>
                  <span data-lang-text="ru">Agar Masjid hi akela raasta ho aur koi doosra raasta na ho, to bina baithe jaldi guzar jaana jaiz hai.</span>
                  <span data-lang-text="ur">اگر مسجد ہی اکیلا راستہ ہو اور کوئی دوسرا راستہ نہ ہو، تو بغیر بیٹھے جلدی گزر جانا جائز ہے۔</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-nav-row">
              <button class="qa-back" data-goto="categorySelection">&larr; <T en="Back" ru="Wapas" ur="واپس" /></button>
              <button class="qa-restart" data-goto="categorySelection"><T en="New Question" ru="Naya Sawal" ur="نیا سوال" /></button>
            </div>
          </div>

